Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.10,0:00:48.56,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.82,0:00:50.36,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:02.70,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}傷を負った　世界を知った
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.45,0:01:07.71,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}強く儚い果実
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:14.63,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}つきまとう　責任の重たさで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.97,0:01:19.14,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}熟れ落ちて　土へと還る
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.06,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.81,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:29.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}この血の滾りを解放してけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.02,0:01:30.02,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}そこにいますか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:34.94,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}衝突に戦々恐々　降り立つ墮天使
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.45,0:01:40.20,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}早々に早熟な実も　食らい盡くすの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:45.91,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}もがく度に　蒼穹に聴いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:49.13,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}君を確かめた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:49.96,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}あっけない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.76,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}無い無い　馴れ合い　有り余った慟哭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:59.09,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}葛藤に混亂していく　今を生きて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:05.98,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(960,3)}それでもまだ　僕らは目指した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.52,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\fs45\pos(960,54)}Follow me Follow you　痛みでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:10.15,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　通じ合えば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.86,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you　何処まででも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.32,OPJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,300)}Follow me Follow you
